channel.title: Ports Randomly Don't Work Anymore
channel.description:
My ports were working for months. Now they don't.
- I have them in the firewall
- I have them forwarded correctly
- I HAVE a static Ip
The odd part is when I host on my laptop they all work fine. But when I try on my computer the host computer they don't.... Help?
